Bundle

A bundle of documentation 

<bundle>
  <file src=.. title=.. >
    <file>...recursion...<file>
  </file>
  <title/>
  <subject/>
  <version/>
  <description/>
  <projectName/>
  <projectLogo/>
  <companyName/>
  <companyLogo/>
</bundle>

bundle

A bundle of files to form a complete document

Element Type Description
file* List<BundleFile> (Many) The files to include in the bundle
title String No description.
subject String No description.
version String No description.
description String No description.
projectName String The name of the project.
projectLogo String The location of an image file that represents the project logo.
companyName String The name of the entity that is responsible for the content of the document, or a copyright holder.
companyLogo String The location of an image file that represents the company logo.

file

A file to be included in the bundle

Attribute Type Description
src String The source filename
title String No description.
Element Type Description
file* List<BundleFile> (Many) The files to include as sub-items
